name: DownbytheBay
0:
”Alexa, play Down by the Bay”
”Alexa, ask Down by the Bay for whale”
”Have you ever seen a mosquito?”
skdetail:
This skill contains: dynamic content.
Invocation Name: down by the bay
des:
Come sing "Down by the Bay" in an interactive sing-along! When the the song goes "have you ever seen a...", you can suggest an animal name, and hear a song verse with a silly rhyme. 

This skill recognizes 70 different animal names. Try suggesting "whale", "cat", "mosquito", "frog", "alpaca", "elk", and more. If you can't think of an animal, say "I don't know" and we'll suggest one for you.
priv: The developer reported that this skill does not collect personal information.
